        <p class="bodytext" >If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us by writing to us at <a href="mailto:<?php echo SITE_EMAIL; ?>" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="email_link"><?php echo SITE_EMAIL; ?></a> or by mail at 1816 Crowchild, Trail NW, Suite, 700 Calgary, Alberta, Canada, T2M 3 YZ.</p>
